videos.description: Butler storms all the way back to take their first lead of the game since being up 9-8 after Sean McDermott nails a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McDermott 3 brings Butler back from 18-point deficit

videos.description: Butler continues its hot shooting in the 2nd half against Xavier as Kelan Martin hits back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Martin hits back-to-back 3s to put Butler ahead

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett sinks a pull-up 3-pointer in the final 2 minutes to give Xavier a comfortable lead.
videos.headline: Bluiett hits clutch 3

videos.description: Sean McDermott hits tough 3-pointer during final minute of play to lower Xavier's lead to 1.
videos.headline: McDermott pulls Butler within 1 late

videos.description: Butler's Kamar Baldwin splashes a 3 with under 20 seconds left to play to tie the game at 84-84.
videos.headline: Baldwin sends it to OT

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett adds to Xavier's lead in overtime with a long 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bluiett drains a deep 3 in OT
